    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors achieve required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Level 1 against a required Level 2 due to single test condition; this shortfall is accepted given Medium model influence, corroborating multi-laboratory experimental data, and quantitative QoI agreement within 2.1% across all three outputs. Overall credibility profile is judged adequate to support regulatory submission for a Class II device at Medium assurance level. The stale material property dataset (vintage 2025-02-17, predating model revision 2025-03-10) was reviewed; the revision was assessed as not material to the dataset's relevance. No formal re-validation of the dataset against the revised model was performed.",
